how to write map reduce job:
http://dongxicheng.org/mapreduce/hadoop-streaming-programming/
Hadoop Streaming:
Hadoop streaming is a utility that comes with the Hadoop distribution. 
The utility allows you to create and run Map/Reduce jobs with any executable or script 
as the mapper and/or the reducer.


